      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and daily utility. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Deep Sea Blue metallic; the paint retains a deep luster, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin appointed in Charcoal leather. The seats are in great shape, with only slight creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all electronic components\u2014including the premium navigation system and dual-zone climate control\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is sound and ready for the road. It features a complete service history, with a recent oil change, new brake pads, and a fresh set of all-season tires. The engine runs smoothly without any hesitation, and the transmission provides crisp, reliable shifts. This car offers a premium driving experience for someone looking for quality and reliability without the new-car price tag.",
